text: Limites of driganhurste andlang pillis þanen on þe olde Gore an soan Roanleighe on þe olde hege rewe so up endlang humbers bitwixe douningleighe.
Þanen on crichhulle and soa bi linen bitwixe abbingleie and soa on Doultingstrem up endlanges at Winterwelle of þan Welle on lincombesleighe on þe rizte on the stanleie Wal.
Þanen on croppanhulle and soa endlang dich on trindleaie mideward.
Þanen on rizt on midden merkesburi.

Þanen endlang weies on Ramer þanen estrizt endlang pathes on þan olden fosse andlang fosse south on pulle a doune bi pulle on lutletone south op on pennard and soa bi Wyrt taman West to Weie endelang weies north est on pil.
